quran[12{c,v,t}:
16,15,uss ne zameen mein pahoron ki maikhain garh den taakay zameen tum ko le kar dhalak nah jaye is ne daal riya jari kiye aur qudrati rastay banaye taakay tum hadaayat pao
16,16,"is ne zameen mein rasta bitanay wali alamtain rakh den, aur taron se bhi log hadaayat paate hain"
16,17,"phir kya woh jo peda karta hai aur woh jo kuch bhi peda nahi karte, dono yaksaa hain? kya tum hosh mein nahi atay ?"
16,18,"agar tum Allah ki nematon ko ginna chaho to gun nahi satke, haqeeqat yeh hai ke woh bara hi dar guzar karne wala aur Raheem hai"
16,19,halaank woh tumahray khulay se bhi waaqif hai aur chupay se bhi
16,20,"aur woh doosri hastiyan jinhein Allah ko chore kar log pkarte hain, woh kisi cheez ki bhi khaaliq nahi hain balkay khud makhlooq hain"
16,21,murda hain nah ke zindah aur un ko kuch maloom nahi hai ke inhen kab ( dobarah zindah kar ke ) uthaya jaye ga
16,22,tumhara khuda bas aik hi khuda hai magar jo log akhirat ko nahi mantay unn ke dilon mein inkaar bas kar reh gaya hai aur woh ghamand mein par gay hain
16,23,Allah yaqeenan inn ke sab kartoot jaanta hai chupay hue bhi aur khulay hue bhi woh unn logon ko hargiz pasand nahi karta jo ghuroor nafs mein mubtala hon
16,24,"aur jab koi un se puchta hai ke tumahray rab ne yeh kya cheez nazil ki hai, to kehte hain"" aji woh to aglay waqton ki farsodah kahaniyan hain """
16,25,"yeh baatein woh is liye karte hain ke qayamat ke roz apne boojh bhi poooray athayin, aur sath sath kuch unn logon ke boojh bhi samaiten jinhein yeh Bar banaye jahalat gumraah kar rahay hain dekho! kaisi sakht zimma daari hai jo yeh apne sir le rahay hain"
16,26,"inn se pehlay bhi bohat se log ( haq ko neecha dikhaane ke liye ) aisi hi makaryan kar chuke hain, to dekh lau ke Allah ne unn ke makr ki imarat jarr se ukhaar pehnki aur is ki chhat oopar se un ke sir par aa rahi aur aisay rukh se un par azaab aaya jidhar se is ke anay ka unn ko gumaan taq nah tha"
